1
00:00:11,010 --> 00:00:13,640
(Hey, Zhou Shuyi.)

2
00:00:15,420 --> 00:00:19,120
(Do you know why being in 1st place
is important to me?)

3
00:00:23,270 --> 00:00:29,970
(Driving forward with reckless abandon)

4
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:38,760
(I only wish to stay somewhere
where you can see me.)

5
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:42,000
(Can you please don't push me away?)

6
00:00:47,930 --> 00:00:52,230
(Can you look at me?)

7
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:08,780
=No.1 For You=

8
00:01:08,935 --> 00:01:11,638
(It's a wonderful thing
to have childhood friends)

9
00:01:11,638 --> 00:01:13,406
(who grow up together with you.)

10
00:01:14,107 --> 00:01:15,675
(But sometimes,)

11
00:01:15,675 --> 00:01:17,911
(a three-way company doesn't work.)

12
00:01:17,911 --> 00:01:18,878
(For example,)

13
00:01:18,878 --> 00:01:20,113
(being in love.)

14
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:23,083
(My father always tells me)

15
00:01:23,083 --> 00:01:24,617
(that failure is natural,)

16
00:01:24,617 --> 00:01:26,152
(and that you're a man if you succeed.)

17
00:01:26,719 --> 00:01:29,122
(Back then, he traveled from Japan
to Taiwan, China,)

18
00:01:29,122 --> 00:01:32,025
(and won my mother's heart
with this attitude.)

19
00:01:37,964 --> 00:01:39,566
(I made a vow to my lucky charm.)

20
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:44,204
(As long as I win
the Swimming Club Newbie PK match,)

21
00:01:45,105 --> 00:01:46,973
(I will accomplish something great,)

22
00:01:47,674 --> 00:01:50,710
(and turn our friendship into
a love relationship.)

23
00:01:52,612 --> 00:01:54,681
(Sorry about that, Fang Zhengwen.)

24
00:01:54,681 --> 00:01:56,683
(I have to get into a relationship
before you.)

25
00:01:57,750 --> 00:01:59,085
(Jiang Yuxin,)

26
00:01:59,085 --> 00:02:00,487
(just wait for my confession.)

27
00:02:01,254 --> 00:02:03,289
(Let's welcome the most important day
for me, Zhou Shuyi,)

28
00:02:03,289 --> 00:02:04,791
(together before my graduation.)

29
00:02:04,791 --> 00:02:05,592
You can do it!

30
00:02:05,825 --> 00:02:06,593
You can do it!

31
00:02:09,662 --> 00:02:10,797
Okay, change sides.

32
00:02:12,332 --> 00:02:13,366
What do you think? Are you confident?

33
00:02:13,366 --> 00:02:14,067
What about you?

34
00:02:14,067 --> 00:02:15,401
Good luck, newbie.

35
00:02:16,569 --> 00:02:18,638
The top swimmer of the swimming club.

36
00:02:18,638 --> 00:02:20,540
1st place is definitely yours.

37
00:02:21,441 --> 00:02:23,443
Shuyi, your swimming cap.

38
00:02:24,644 --> 00:02:25,778
Shuyi, your swimming goggles.

39
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,414
Shuyi, you can do it.

40
00:02:28,414 --> 00:02:29,382
Thank you.

41
00:02:29,382 --> 00:02:30,483
He's so handsome!

42
00:02:31,885 --> 00:02:33,086
You're so popular.

43
00:02:33,086 --> 00:02:33,753
Not bad at all.

44
00:02:33,753 --> 00:02:34,888
Are you confident that you can win?

45
00:02:34,888 --> 00:02:35,855
Of course.

46
00:02:36,356 --> 00:02:38,191
I just need to use 40% of my full power

47
00:02:38,191 --> 00:02:39,893
(Freshman Joining)
for such a competition.

48
00:02:39,893 --> 00:02:41,294
(Freshman Joining)
Don't get ahead of yourself here.

49
00:02:41,294 --> 00:02:43,029
I'm Zhou Shuyi, you know?

50
00:02:43,029 --> 00:02:43,663
Fine.

51
00:02:43,663 --> 00:02:45,265
Remember, focus.

52
00:02:45,265 --> 00:02:45,999
And relax.

53
00:02:46,566 --> 00:02:47,867
Shide, tonight...

54
00:02:47,867 --> 00:02:50,036
Gao Shide, you're so handsome!

55
00:02:53,873 --> 00:02:54,974
What are you doing here?

56
00:03:01,548 --> 00:03:02,882
(What is he doing here?)

57
00:03:02,882 --> 00:03:04,918
(Is he trying to spoil my plan?)

58
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:08,154
(Oh, no! My leg is cramping up!)

59
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,161
(Are you okay?)

60
00:03:15,161 --> 00:03:16,663
(I'm okay.)

61
00:03:17,597 --> 00:03:18,765
(But your leg is...)

62
00:03:18,765 --> 00:03:19,933
(I'll pull you up.)

63
00:03:19,933 --> 00:03:20,900
(No need for that.)

64
00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:22,101
(I don't need your help.)

65
00:03:22,101 --> 00:03:23,503
(Go away.)

66
00:03:28,141 --> 00:03:29,576
(Some people say that setbacks)

67
00:03:29,576 --> 00:03:31,477
(are our enemies,)

68
00:03:31,711 --> 00:03:33,680
(and failures are the steps
that impede us in life.)

69
00:03:36,149 --> 00:03:36,816
(To me,)

70
00:03:36,816 --> 00:03:38,985
(no matter if it's rivals or setbacks,)

71
00:03:38,985 --> 00:03:40,553
(I only think of one name.)

72
00:03:40,553 --> 00:03:42,388
(Gao Shide.)

73
00:03:45,225 --> 00:03:46,893
(From primary school to junior high
and senior high,)

74
00:03:46,893 --> 00:03:48,194
(no matter what kind of competition
I participated in,)

75
00:03:48,461 --> 00:03:50,163
(whether it's English, essay-writing,)

76
00:03:50,163 --> 00:03:52,332
(Go, debate, sprint, and so on,)

77
00:03:52,966 --> 00:03:53,600
(because of him,)

78
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:54,901
(I was always in 2nd place.)

79
00:04:10,717 --> 00:04:11,818
Shide.

80
00:04:11,818 --> 00:04:14,787
Shide, here.

81
00:04:15,822 --> 00:04:18,591
I bought it for you. You must finish it.

82
00:04:18,591 --> 00:04:19,592
I'm sure you'll like it.

83
00:04:19,592 --> 00:04:20,293
This is yours.

84
00:04:25,150 --> 00:04:26,850
(First place, Gao Shide, 698,
Second place, Zhou Shuyi, 697)

85
00:04:36,075 --> 00:04:38,278
(I don't like losing.)

86
00:04:38,278 --> 00:04:40,246
(But ever since his appearance,)

87
00:04:40,246 --> 00:04:42,348
(I was always)

88
00:04:42,348 --> 00:04:47,654
(the runner-up!)

89
00:04:58,431 --> 00:04:59,399
Hey.

90
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:00,199
What are you doing?

91
00:05:00,566 --> 00:05:01,501
What happened?

92
00:05:02,769 --> 00:05:04,037
I'm fine.

93
00:05:04,904 --> 00:05:05,605
Hey.

94
00:05:07,807 --> 00:05:09,676
He didn't even thank you.

95
00:05:11,477 --> 00:05:12,845
Thank you for saving Shuyi.

96
00:05:14,681 --> 00:05:16,416
Put it on. Don't catch a cold.

97
00:05:38,771 --> 00:05:39,939
You'll be fine.

98
00:05:40,606 --> 00:05:41,741
Safety first.

99
00:05:42,608 --> 00:05:43,710
Don't be upset.

100
00:05:50,850 --> 00:05:52,618
Falling into the pool
is just a small deal.

101
00:05:52,618 --> 00:05:53,853
Don't cry.

102
00:05:53,853 --> 00:05:55,321
Now, the entire school
knows who you are.

103
00:05:55,688 --> 00:05:56,322
You're famous now.

104
00:05:56,322 --> 00:05:57,757
Who's crying?

105
00:05:58,324 --> 00:05:59,225
Darn it.

106
00:06:00,093 --> 00:06:02,228
He embarrassed me in front of everyone.

107
00:06:02,595 --> 00:06:04,497
You fell into the pool yourself.

108
00:06:04,497 --> 00:06:05,298
Just forget it.

109
00:06:05,998 --> 00:06:07,133
You guys have been good friends

110
00:06:07,133 --> 00:06:07,834
for a long time.

111
00:06:07,834 --> 00:06:09,602
Who said we are good friends?

112
00:06:10,803 --> 00:06:12,238
That's ridiculous.

113
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:14,974
We studied in the same primary school,
junior high, and senior high.

114
00:06:15,475 --> 00:06:17,510
I thought I wouldn't need to see him
in university.

115
00:06:18,177 --> 00:06:19,712
I didn't expect him to
make a school transfer

116
00:06:19,712 --> 00:06:22,982
to our university
during his sophomore year.

117
00:06:23,516 --> 00:06:25,084
I've endured this until my senior year.

118
00:06:25,718 --> 00:06:27,587
I will never forgive him.

119
00:06:27,587 --> 00:06:28,688
That's right.

120
00:06:28,688 --> 00:06:30,523
I'll definitely support you
until the end.

121
00:06:30,890 --> 00:06:32,225
Let's show Gao Shide
who's the boss here.

122
00:06:39,766 --> 00:06:40,867
What's the matter?

123
00:06:45,571 --> 00:06:47,106
Bingwei, are you done?

124
00:06:47,106 --> 00:06:48,508
Almost. Wait a second.

125
00:06:48,508 --> 00:06:49,642
They're coming. Hurry up.

126
00:06:51,043 --> 00:06:52,211
Hurry.

127
00:06:52,545 --> 00:06:53,746
I'm done.

128
00:06:55,281 --> 00:06:56,215
Let's go.

129
00:07:05,958 --> 00:07:06,926
Shide,

130
00:07:06,926 --> 00:07:08,327
lend it to me.

131
00:07:09,262 --> 00:07:10,396
Okay.

132
00:07:10,396 --> 00:07:11,431
Thanks.

133
00:07:17,837 --> 00:07:18,337
Who did this?

134
00:07:18,337 --> 00:07:19,405
Darn it.

135
00:07:19,405 --> 00:07:20,773
Let's think of something else.

136
00:07:20,773 --> 00:07:21,507
Okay.

137
00:07:23,276 --> 00:07:23,976
Who did this?

138
00:07:32,785 --> 00:07:33,686
Nice shot.

139
00:07:33,686 --> 00:07:34,454
Shide.

140
00:07:35,955 --> 00:07:37,423
Your layup was nice.

141
00:07:37,423 --> 00:07:38,558
-Good job.
-You blocked him.

142
00:07:41,861 --> 00:07:42,595
Here you go.

143
00:07:45,598 --> 00:07:46,933
It's free.

144
00:07:46,933 --> 00:07:48,000
We shouldn't let it go to waste.

145
00:07:50,436 --> 00:07:51,604
It's a bomb.

146
00:07:52,138 --> 00:07:53,339
I just bought this shirt.

147
00:08:01,650 --> 00:08:03,250
(Silly)

148
00:08:03,382 --> 00:08:04,617
Pass me the towel.

149
00:08:08,187 --> 00:08:09,622
I'm pretty unlucky lately.

150
00:09:08,447 --> 00:09:09,348
That was nice.

151
00:09:10,883 --> 00:09:11,717
Bravo.

152
00:09:24,063 --> 00:09:27,033
You did the prank, right?

153
00:09:27,033 --> 00:09:28,000
What prank?

154
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,268
I don't know what you're talking about.

155
00:09:34,407 --> 00:09:35,107
What?

156
00:09:39,979 --> 00:09:41,347
You smell like talcum powder.

157
00:09:42,448 --> 00:09:43,249
Stop lying.

158
00:09:43,249 --> 00:09:44,016
I threw it away long ago.

159
00:09:44,016 --> 00:09:45,217
Threw what away?

160
00:10:05,571 --> 00:10:07,907
Spreading chili powder
in his swimming trunks,

161
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:13,613
calling him without saying anything,

162
00:10:16,082 --> 00:10:18,184
waxing his eyebrows,

163
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:22,254
trimming his nostrils in secret,

164
00:10:24,757 --> 00:10:27,059
sticking chewing gum on his chair...

165
00:10:27,059 --> 00:10:28,828
(A million ways to prank Gao Shide)

166
00:10:28,828 --> 00:10:29,829
(A million ways to prank Gao Shide)
Are you done?

167
00:10:29,829 --> 00:10:31,397
(A million ways to prank Gao Shide)
We started this since 3 p.m.

168
00:10:31,397 --> 00:10:32,865
(A million ways to prank Gao Shide)
Yeah, we're running out of inspiration.

169
00:10:33,299 --> 00:10:34,834
Are we pranking him?
Or is he pranking us?

170
00:10:34,834 --> 00:10:36,187
(A million ways to prank Gao Shide)

171
00:10:37,837 --> 00:10:39,939
Why don't we just hire goons
to beat him up?

172
00:10:41,407 --> 00:10:42,608
Have you lost your mind?

173
00:10:42,608 --> 00:10:43,709
To think that you're in
the Faculty of Law.

174
00:10:43,709 --> 00:10:44,977
How could you come up
with something like that?

175
00:10:44,977 --> 00:10:46,045
They're smart.

176
00:10:46,045 --> 00:10:47,313
They'll hide their identities.

177
00:10:49,815 --> 00:10:51,250
I think

178
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:52,051
we should forget it.

179
00:10:52,585 --> 00:10:53,753
We're already in our senior year.

180
00:10:54,286 --> 00:10:55,388
Just endure it and graduate.

181
00:10:56,055 --> 00:10:59,158
That's precisely why we need to do
something memorable before we graduate.

182
00:10:59,625 --> 00:11:01,260
Do you think I'll lose to him?

183
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:02,895
I've already come up with so many ideas.

184
00:11:03,262 --> 00:11:04,664
That's not what I mean.

185
00:11:05,564 --> 00:11:06,932
All of us are adults.

186
00:11:06,932 --> 00:11:08,567
Can't we just talk this over?

187
00:11:08,567 --> 00:11:09,301
Yeah.

188
00:11:09,301 --> 00:11:10,102
I don't care.

189
00:11:10,102 --> 00:11:11,070
I must prank him somehow.

190
00:11:11,504 --> 00:11:12,471
Shuyi.

191
00:11:15,708 --> 00:11:16,776
Are we done?

192
00:11:17,743 --> 00:11:19,211
Remember to take a photo of it.

193
00:11:31,957 --> 00:11:34,994
Bingwei took a blurry shot
of the pranking ideas.

194
00:11:37,296 --> 00:11:39,532
I need to prank Gao Shide somehow.

195
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:42,968
Fang Zhengwen, hurry up.

196
00:11:42,968 --> 00:11:44,370
Fine.

197
00:11:45,638 --> 00:11:46,972
What's the matter?

198
00:11:47,273 --> 00:11:48,374
You're being so mysterious.

199
00:11:48,374 --> 00:11:49,875
I have something to tell you.

200
00:11:54,780 --> 00:11:56,382
Fang Zhengwen, do you hate me?

201
00:11:57,483 --> 00:11:58,250
Of course not.

202
00:11:59,251 --> 00:12:00,252
So,

203
00:12:00,252 --> 00:12:01,554
you don't hate me?

204
00:12:01,987 --> 00:12:04,256
What are you saying?
How could I hate you?

205
00:12:04,256 --> 00:12:05,524
If so, does that mean you like me?

206
00:12:05,524 --> 00:12:07,226
Didn't I tell you already...

207
00:12:08,527 --> 00:12:10,062
It's because I like you.

208
00:12:10,563 --> 00:12:11,667
Besides my thesis,

209
00:12:11,667 --> 00:12:14,266
you're the most important thing
to me before graduation.

210
00:12:15,735 --> 00:12:18,304
If you don't hate me,

211
00:12:18,304 --> 00:12:20,139
do you want to be my boyfriend?

212
00:12:22,208 --> 00:12:22,908
Shuyi?

213
00:12:22,908 --> 00:12:24,009
What are you doing here?

214
00:12:24,810 --> 00:12:26,479
I'm so glad.

215
00:12:26,479 --> 00:12:28,714
Finally, we have some great news.

216
00:12:28,714 --> 00:12:30,483
The three of us grew up together.

217
00:12:30,483 --> 00:12:31,884
Now, you two will date each other.

218
00:12:31,884 --> 00:12:33,219
This is great.

219
00:12:34,653 --> 00:12:35,855
Hurry and say yes to her.

220
00:12:37,389 --> 00:12:39,024
I was worried that this tomboy

221
00:12:39,024 --> 00:12:40,760
might be left on the shelf.

222
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:41,594
Shuyi, I don't know...

223
00:12:41,594 --> 00:12:44,029
I can rest at ease
when you're dating her.

224
00:12:45,431 --> 00:12:47,199
I want to celebrate
this occasion for you guys.

225
00:12:47,199 --> 00:12:48,601
What about tonight?

226
00:12:49,435 --> 00:12:50,503
-Shuyi...
-Tonight, okay?

227
00:12:51,203 --> 00:12:51,904
8 p.m.

228
00:12:52,805 --> 00:12:54,340
-Shuyi...
-See you later.

229
00:14:09,448 --> 00:14:10,883
Zhengwen is a fool.

230
00:14:13,018 --> 00:14:14,186
Yuxin is a fool.

231
00:14:18,123 --> 00:14:20,092
Both of them are fools.

232
00:14:22,494 --> 00:14:23,963
I worked so hard.

233
00:14:27,733 --> 00:14:29,568
Why are you guys doing this to me?

234
00:14:59,899 --> 00:15:02,334
You said this lucky charm
was custom-made.

235
00:15:11,243 --> 00:15:12,845
How is this lucky?

236
00:17:02,688 --> 00:17:04,056
What's wrong with you?

237
00:17:04,056 --> 00:17:05,357
Do you have a death wish?

238
00:17:05,357 --> 00:17:06,225
What's wrong with you?

239
00:17:06,225 --> 00:17:07,326
Why did you kiss me?

240
00:17:10,496 --> 00:17:11,864
Who told you to stay underwater?

241
00:17:14,233 --> 00:17:15,401
That's none of your business.

242
00:17:15,401 --> 00:17:16,435
You're such a busybody.

243
00:17:17,236 --> 00:17:18,704
Do you like Jiang Yuxin that much?

244
00:17:19,405 --> 00:17:20,506
You wanted to take your own life

245
00:17:20,506 --> 00:17:22,174
after hearing that she would
date Fang Zhengwen?

246
00:17:23,475 --> 00:17:25,244
How did you know that I like her?

247
00:17:25,477 --> 00:17:26,845
Were you keeping me under surveillance?

248
00:17:29,615 --> 00:17:30,749
I always have my eyes on you.

249
00:17:35,421 --> 00:17:37,156
I'm sure you were thinking of ways
to keep on dominating me

250
00:17:37,156 --> 00:17:38,557
and make me the runner-up,

251
00:17:38,557 --> 00:17:39,858
so that you can mock me, huh?

252
00:17:41,293 --> 00:17:43,162
I knew you were up to no good.

253
00:17:43,162 --> 00:17:44,530
Here you go.

254
00:17:44,530 --> 00:17:45,431
Are you happy now?

255
00:17:45,431 --> 00:17:46,465
Scram!

256
00:17:51,470 --> 00:17:52,671
Zhou Shuyi.

257
00:17:53,338 --> 00:17:54,973
Do you want me to beat you up?

258
00:17:55,741 --> 00:17:56,408
Scram.

259
00:18:29,374 --> 00:18:32,611
(Some people say that having a crush is
the only relationship that won't fail.)

260
00:18:33,112 --> 00:18:34,113
(Nonsense.)

261
00:18:34,113 --> 00:18:36,448
(When your crush is
dating someone else,)

262
00:18:36,448 --> 00:18:38,584
(especially your childhood friend,)

263
00:18:39,318 --> 00:18:41,787
(it's more heartbreaking than
getting dumped.)

264
00:18:41,787 --> 00:18:43,689
(The pain is so bad)

265
00:18:43,689 --> 00:18:45,390
(that you'll feel like
destroying the world.)

266
00:18:45,958 --> 00:18:48,160
(It's so painful that a clear weather)

267
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:50,229
(looks like inclemency to you.)

268
00:18:50,662 --> 00:18:52,397
(As the saying goes,
clouds gather before a storm.)

269
00:19:08,881 --> 00:19:11,683
(The most painful thing about falling
out of love isn't losing your beloved.)

270
00:19:12,017 --> 00:19:13,652
(It's that you'll start to
doubt yourself)

271
00:19:14,186 --> 00:19:15,554
(and think that you aren't good enough)

272
00:19:15,554 --> 00:19:16,955
(for people to like you.)

