I'll add some meat for you.

552
00:36:46,170 --> 00:36:48,739
Why are you making spicy hot pot
when you can't take spicy food?

553
00:36:49,874 --> 00:36:51,108
It's fine as long as you like it.

554
00:36:53,611 --> 00:36:55,146
How did you know I like spicy hot pot?

555
00:36:56,781 --> 00:36:58,182
I know everything about you.

556
00:37:03,221 --> 00:37:04,388
So,

557
00:37:04,956 --> 00:37:05,890
thank you for helping me.

558
00:37:12,930 --> 00:37:14,765
They might've discovered my secret

559
00:37:14,765 --> 00:37:16,234
if you didn't help me out just now.

560
00:37:20,204 --> 00:37:21,839
Is the shrimp done?

561
00:37:22,506 --> 00:37:23,341
Yeah.

562
00:37:34,919 --> 00:37:36,654
Seems like you don't mind

563
00:37:39,090 --> 00:37:40,391
losing Jiang Yuxin that much now.

564
00:37:41,259 --> 00:37:42,693
I guess so.

565
00:37:43,794 --> 00:37:44,695
Thanks.

566
00:37:52,203 --> 00:37:53,204
Actually,

567
00:37:54,005 --> 00:37:55,139
compared to falling out of love,

568
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:57,341
it's even more heartbreaking when

569
00:37:58,376 --> 00:38:00,211
you don't even have a chance
to fight for it.

570
00:38:01,045 --> 00:38:02,213
It ended

571
00:38:02,613 --> 00:38:03,748
even before it started.

572
00:38:05,116 --> 00:38:07,285
What will you do if the person you like

573
00:38:07,285 --> 00:38:08,219
likes someone else?

574
00:38:11,155 --> 00:38:12,156
Me?

575
00:38:18,262 --> 00:38:19,363
I will

576
00:38:20,031 --> 00:38:21,599
ruin their relationship

577
00:38:22,266 --> 00:38:23,567
and take advantage of it.

578
00:38:28,105 --> 00:38:29,507
You must be joking.

579
00:38:32,176 --> 00:38:33,477
Yeah.

580
00:38:53,631 --> 00:38:54,765
Gao Shide,

581
00:38:55,633 --> 00:38:56,734
can I apply for leave

582
00:38:57,034 --> 00:38:58,169
as your attendant?

583
00:39:03,007 --> 00:39:04,075
Where are we going?

584
00:39:04,075 --> 00:39:05,176
I thought you were heading to class?

585
00:39:05,176 --> 00:39:06,110
Slow down.

586
00:39:06,544 --> 00:39:07,678
Slow down.

587
00:39:15,319 --> 00:39:17,588
Do you have a death wish?

588
00:39:20,358 --> 00:39:22,259
You knew you had a weak stomach.

589
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,828
Why did you take spicy hot pot?

590
00:39:24,695 --> 00:39:25,696
Have you lost your mind?

591
00:39:38,008 --> 00:39:39,377
Zhou Shuyi,

592
00:39:41,145 --> 00:39:42,680
the gastric medicine
can only relieve your pain temporarily.

593
00:39:42,680 --> 00:39:43,848
You still need to visit a doctor.

594
00:39:53,824 --> 00:39:56,427
Avoid oily and salty food this week.

595
00:39:57,728 --> 00:39:58,729
However, if you wish to die,

596
00:40:00,364 --> 00:40:01,966
you can try taking spicy hot pot again.

597
00:40:03,167 --> 00:40:05,636
You're intimidating your patient.

598
00:40:05,636 --> 00:40:07,805
What's wrong with this school doctor?

599
00:40:08,740 --> 00:40:09,840
(Pei Shouyi)

600
00:40:13,744 --> 00:40:15,446
Are you sure he is the one?

601
00:40:20,518 --> 00:40:22,119
You...

602
00:40:22,119 --> 00:40:23,154
You can take a break.

603
00:40:33,531 --> 00:40:34,665
Great.

604
00:40:34,665 --> 00:40:36,167
I'm going to buy a pack of cigarettes.

605
00:40:36,167 --> 00:40:38,402
You can rest here.

606
00:40:41,839 --> 00:40:43,808
What's wrong with them?

607
00:40:44,074 --> 00:40:45,242
It seemed like they knew each other.

608
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:51,615
Why did you say that in front of him?

609
00:40:53,417 --> 00:40:54,785
To have fun.

610
00:40:55,386 --> 00:40:57,421
So, you can actually have fun
when you have a mood disorder?

611
00:41:00,858 --> 00:41:02,460
As long as it's interesting.

612
00:41:05,896 --> 00:41:08,566
So, that's my future cousin-in-law, huh?

613
00:41:08,566 --> 00:41:10,134
He's a fine-looking man.

614
00:41:10,134 --> 00:41:12,069
Isn't that great?

615
00:41:12,069 --> 00:41:14,004
He's just an eye candy.

616
00:41:14,004 --> 00:41:15,940
It's because you can't
see his kind nature.

617
00:41:15,940 --> 00:41:18,242
I can't.

618
00:41:18,242 --> 00:41:20,110
Maybe

619
00:41:20,611 --> 00:41:22,279
I need to understand him
on a deeper level.

620
00:41:23,380 --> 00:41:24,114
No need for that.

621
00:41:25,516 --> 00:41:26,917
He'll never fall for me.

622
00:41:31,522 --> 00:41:32,790
Why did you fall for him then?

623
00:41:34,658 --> 00:41:35,793
Without him,

624
00:41:35,793 --> 00:41:37,595
I might not get to where I am today.

625
00:41:38,596 --> 00:41:40,631
I encountered him
when I was in Fifth Grade.

626
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,168
Back then,

627
00:41:44,969 --> 00:41:46,437
my parents just got divorced.

628
00:41:46,971 --> 00:41:49,240
I had a rough time.

629
00:41:49,874 --> 00:41:52,009
I was only a primary school student.

630
00:41:52,009 --> 00:41:53,077
How could I possibly understand

631
00:41:53,077 --> 00:41:55,246
the fact that my father
abandoned the family?

632
00:41:56,914 --> 00:41:58,883
But I knew that my mother

633
00:41:58,883 --> 00:42:00,451
had it rougher than me.

634
00:42:01,919 --> 00:42:03,454
That's why I pretended to be strong.

635
00:42:05,489 --> 00:42:07,525
But sometimes, I couldn't
keep up with the pretense.

636
00:42:15,933 --> 00:42:16,901
Hey.

637
00:42:16,901 --> 00:42:18,335
What's the matter with you?

638
00:42:18,335 --> 00:42:19,403
Are you okay?

639
00:42:27,444 --> 00:42:28,078
Hey.

640
00:42:28,913 --> 00:42:31,015
Your mucus and drool
are all over the place.

641
00:42:31,015 --> 00:42:32,116
You look terrible.

642
00:42:32,416 --> 00:42:33,918
My father...

643
00:42:35,085 --> 00:42:37,321
He abandoned me and my mother.

644
00:42:40,491 --> 00:42:42,393
At least you still have a mother.

645
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:46,630
My mother already went to heaven.

646
00:42:55,339 --> 00:42:56,540
Or,

647
00:42:56,540 --> 00:42:58,475
do you want my father?

648
00:42:58,475 --> 00:43:01,211
Bad things always happen
when I spend time with him.

649
00:43:02,947 --> 00:43:05,182
How could you give
your father away like that?

650
00:43:14,959 --> 00:43:15,960
Why don't I

651
00:43:16,894 --> 00:43:19,063
give myself to you then?

652
00:43:19,063 --> 00:43:20,931
Just come to me when you need me.

653
00:43:20,931 --> 00:43:22,399
You can treat me as your father.

654
00:43:26,203 --> 00:43:28,305
Good boy. You look better
when you smile.

655
00:43:28,606 --> 00:43:29,773
Shuyi.

656
00:43:31,008 --> 00:43:32,376
Where have you been?

657
00:43:41,518 --> 00:43:43,721
Come to me when you want to cry.
I'll lend you my shoulders.

658
00:43:44,688 --> 00:43:45,990
I'm Zhou Shuyi.

659
00:43:45,990 --> 00:43:47,925
I'm studying at Sanqiao Primary School,
Grade Five, Class One.

660
00:43:48,425 --> 00:43:49,460
See you.

661
00:43:50,527 --> 00:43:52,329
(Although it was proven)

662
00:43:52,329 --> 00:43:55,866
(that he did so out of curiosity)

663
00:43:55,866 --> 00:43:58,002
(as he couldn't recognize me)

664
00:43:58,002 --> 00:43:59,803
(after I transferred to his school,)

665
00:44:00,537 --> 00:44:04,441
(he did save me that afternoon.)

666
00:44:05,776 --> 00:44:06,977
(You have no idea)

667
00:44:06,977 --> 00:44:09,680
(how important his hug
and shoulders were)

668
00:44:09,680 --> 00:44:11,715
(to me)

669
00:44:11,715 --> 00:44:13,217
(at that exact moment.)

670
00:44:46,817 --> 00:44:48,018
I'll head to class first.

671
00:44:50,921 --> 00:44:52,823
I thought you would skip class for him

672
00:44:53,457 --> 00:44:55,225
and make him realize
what you did for him.

673
00:44:56,126 --> 00:44:57,895
After that, you would
use the opportunity

674
00:44:58,962 --> 00:44:59,830
to bend him.

675
00:45:05,803 --> 00:45:08,072
I just wish to become his friend
before we graduate.

676
00:45:09,640 --> 00:45:11,108
Good.

677
00:45:11,108 --> 00:45:13,744
You'll follow your mother to America
after graduating anyway.

678
00:45:14,478 --> 00:45:15,646
You shouldn't drag him into this.

679
00:45:17,681 --> 00:45:19,249
I wouldn't even have the chance
to be his friend,

680
00:45:19,249 --> 00:45:21,785
if he didn't fall out of love
in the first place.

681
00:45:23,387 --> 00:45:26,156
So, you're keeping him company
during this period

682
00:45:26,757 --> 00:45:27,491
to repay the favor?

683
00:45:29,460 --> 00:45:31,361
Are you a snow crane?

684
00:45:31,361 --> 00:45:33,330
If you have that much sympathy
floating around,

685
00:45:33,330 --> 00:45:34,965
you should help people
to recycle resources.

686
00:45:35,833 --> 00:45:37,568
Speak for yourself.

687
00:45:37,568 --> 00:45:39,403
Your mug is broken, yet you...

688
00:45:45,309 --> 00:45:46,677
You'll cut your lips.

689
00:45:51,315 --> 00:45:52,516
I'll leave Shuyi to you then.

690
00:46:08,398 --> 00:46:10,200
Okay. That's all for today.

691
00:46:12,770 --> 00:46:13,637
Let's go.

692
00:46:13,637 --> 00:46:15,272
I'm not free.

693
00:46:17,841 --> 00:46:18,575
Shuyi,

694
00:46:19,543 --> 00:46:20,878
are you busy later?

695
00:46:21,411 --> 00:46:22,112
What?

696
00:46:22,813 --> 00:46:25,048
It's been a long time
since we had lunch together.

697
00:46:25,816 --> 00:46:26,884
I have something to do later.

698
00:46:33,323 --> 00:46:35,425
I just want to ask you this.

699
00:46:38,128 --> 00:46:39,797
So,

700
00:46:40,130 --> 00:46:41,632
do you like Yuxin too?

701
00:46:44,468 --> 00:46:47,237
Don't try to give her to me
just because we're buddies.

702
00:46:47,237 --> 00:46:49,273
There should be no issue
since both of you

703
00:46:49,273 --> 00:46:50,374
like each other.

704
00:46:51,508 --> 00:46:52,276
However,

705
00:46:53,544 --> 00:46:55,412
judging by the way
you reacted when you saw us,

706
00:46:56,513 --> 00:46:58,048
are you sure you're okay with it?

707
00:47:01,185 --> 00:47:02,986
Will you give Yuxin to me

708
00:47:03,253 --> 00:47:04,655
if I say I'm not okay with it?

709
00:47:13,063 --> 00:47:14,331
Gao Shide.

710
00:47:14,565 --> 00:47:15,332
Gao Shide!

711
00:47:19,636 --> 00:47:20,938
Is your tummy better now?

712
00:47:23,273 --> 00:47:24,741
Zhengwen looked for me.

713
00:47:25,175 --> 00:47:26,210
Why?

714
00:47:26,610 --> 00:47:28,445
He asked me if I liked Yuxin.

715
00:47:28,846 --> 00:47:30,414
I asked him

716
00:47:30,414 --> 00:47:32,082
if he's willing to give her to me
if I said yes.

717
00:47:32,082 --> 00:47:33,083
Give her to you?

718
00:47:33,917 --> 00:47:35,285
He rejected the notion

719
00:47:35,619 --> 00:47:36,854
without hesitation.

720
00:47:39,156 --> 00:47:41,258
That guy has always been meek.

721
00:47:41,692 --> 00:47:43,760
I never expected him
to have such a strong attitude.

722
00:47:46,864 --> 00:47:48,365
I feel happy.

723
00:47:50,234 --> 00:47:52,236
I hope he'll treat Yuxin well.

724
00:47:52,569 --> 00:47:54,605
If not, I'll definitely beat him up.

725
00:47:57,541 --> 00:47:58,876
You're right.

726
00:48:00,410 --> 00:48:02,613
Time does cure everything.

727
00:48:04,047 --> 00:48:04,748
This is great.

728
00:48:05,282 --> 00:48:05,916
Congratulations.

729
00:48:05,916 --> 00:48:06,550
Alright.

730
00:48:06,550 --> 00:48:08,252
You got it?

731
00:48:09,753 --> 00:48:13,290
Aren't you two the main pillars
of the swimming club?

732
00:48:17,461 --> 00:48:18,428
Do you two want to join

733
00:48:18,428 --> 00:48:21,031
the sending-off party
held by our juniors?

734
00:48:21,031 --> 00:48:24,368
It's a test of courage

735
00:48:24,368 --> 00:48:26,036
held in a windless and dark night.

736
00:48:27,571 --> 00:48:31,174
The bizarre school phenomenon
will be expecting your arrival!

737
00:48:32,876 --> 00:48:33,710
And,

738
00:48:33,710 --> 00:48:34,411
if you guys do join it,

739
00:48:34,411 --> 00:48:35,779
I'm sure our juniors

740
00:48:35,779 --> 00:48:37,915
will be elated, right?

741
00:48:37,915 --> 00:48:39,917
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

742
00:48:40,484 --> 00:48:41,652
I'm not joining.

743
00:48:42,719 --> 00:48:44,955
Don't be like this.

744
00:48:44,955 --> 00:48:46,290
You spent time with him lately.

745
00:48:46,290 --> 00:48:47,758
You didn't spend any time with us.

746
00:48:48,392 --> 00:48:49,359
Listen.

747
00:48:49,359 --> 00:48:52,629
We even prepared an obstacle course.

748
00:48:52,629 --> 00:48:55,265
The winner will get attractive prizes.

749
00:48:55,265 --> 00:48:56,099
And,

750
00:48:56,099 --> 00:48:58,835
we made the challenge
even harder this time.

751
00:48:59,236 --> 00:49:01,238
We'll confiscate your phones.

752
00:49:01,238 --> 00:49:03,106
Your brain cells and guts

753
00:49:03,106 --> 00:49:04,675
will be put to the test!

754
00:49:06,576 --> 00:49:07,377
Come on.

755
00:49:07,377 --> 00:49:10,380
Let's make some memorable memories
before you guys graduate.

756
00:49:10,380 --> 00:49:11,848
What do you guys think?

757
00:49:11,848 --> 00:49:13,550
Sure!

758
00:49:15,385 --> 00:49:18,088
-(A challenge?)
-(Memorable memories?)

759
00:49:22,225 --> 00:49:23,193
(I guess one more is fine.)

760
00:49:23,193 --> 00:49:24,995
(I'll be free once I win!)

761
00:49:33,503 --> 00:49:34,137
Did you guys hear that?

762
00:49:34,137 --> 00:49:35,639
Did you guys hear the footsteps?

763
00:49:35,639 --> 00:49:36,373
Were there footsteps?

764
00:49:36,373 --> 00:49:37,140
What footsteps?

765
00:49:37,140 --> 00:49:38,809
It's coming.

766
00:49:38,809 --> 00:49:40,310
It was terrifying.

767
00:49:41,611 --> 00:49:42,713
I told you guys already.

768
00:49:42,713 --> 00:49:44,014
I wasn't lying.

769
00:49:44,014 --> 00:49:46,683
That's the third person
who came out crying.

770
00:50:20,017 --> 00:50:21,218
What are you doing here?

771
00:50:21,218 --> 00:50:22,986
Were you frightened?

772
00:50:25,188 --> 00:50:26,957
How could you be so adorable?

773
00:50:27,958 --> 00:50:29,559
The juniors came to me.

774
00:50:29,559 --> 00:50:31,828
I was thinking that I could make
your university life memorable for you.

775
00:50:31,828 --> 00:50:34,398
Look, I even disguised myself
as a ghost for you.

776
00:50:34,398 --> 00:50:35,966
So, you're here alone?

777
00:50:37,000 --> 00:50:37,868
If so,

778
00:50:39,002 --> 00:50:41,671
why don't I stay here with you?

779
00:50:45,909 --> 00:50:47,144
You scared me.

780
00:50:47,144 --> 00:50:49,146
What are you doing behind me?

781
00:50:49,146 --> 00:50:50,213
You're the one blocking my path.

782
00:50:51,081 --> 00:50:51,481
Oh.

783
00:50:53,383 --> 00:50:54,484
Let's proceed.

784
00:51:01,591 --> 00:51:02,626
I thought you got over her?

785
00:51:04,728 --> 00:51:07,397
I just feel happy that
they have a great relationship.

786
00:51:08,832 --> 00:51:10,000
You should focus.

787
00:51:10,000 --> 00:51:11,568
This time, I'll defeat you.

788
00:51:20,944 --> 00:51:22,546
(My goodness.)

789
00:51:22,546 --> 00:51:25,715
(Since when was
our school this terrifying?)

790
00:51:25,715 --> 00:51:27,451
(My flashlight is out of battery too.)

791
00:51:30,053 --> 00:51:31,788
(Gao Shide should still be here, right?)

792
00:51:33,890 --> 00:51:35,192
Why are you still here?

793
00:51:35,192 --> 00:51:36,126
Go now.

794
00:51:48,605 --> 00:51:50,073
I...

795
00:51:50,974 --> 00:51:52,342
I'm afraid of ghosts.

796
00:51:54,377 --> 00:51:55,612
I'll go easy on you.

797
00:51:55,612 --> 00:51:57,414
Let's drop the match.

798
00:51:57,414 --> 00:51:59,382
It's pointless for me to win like this.

799
00:51:59,382 --> 00:52:01,251
Let's go through the maze together.

800
00:52:05,489 --> 00:52:06,356
What are you doing?

801
00:52:09,459 --> 00:52:10,460
Will I drag you down?

802
00:52:14,965 --> 00:52:16,766
Don't worry.

803
00:52:17,300 --> 00:52:18,668
I have your back.

804
00:52:27,043 --> 00:52:28,078
Hurry up.

805
00:52:30,147 --> 00:52:31,748
You're a man, for Heaven's sake.

806
00:52:31,748 --> 00:52:32,682
I'll lead you.

807
00:52:46,730 --> 00:52:47,797
Stay in front.

808
00:52:48,198 --> 00:52:49,666
It's scarier at the back.

809
00:52:50,534 --> 00:52:51,368
Are you ready?

810
00:52:52,435 --> 00:52:54,070
Where will Shide go?

811
00:52:55,105 --> 00:52:58,175
What did I say just now?
Did you not hear me?

812
00:52:58,175 --> 00:52:59,743
Hurry up!

813
00:53:00,377 --> 00:53:02,312
I'm begging you guys.

814
00:53:02,312 --> 00:53:03,480
I was wrong.

815
00:53:03,480 --> 00:53:05,582
I used too much strength.

816
00:53:10,854 --> 00:53:11,454
What?

817
00:53:12,389 --> 00:53:13,423
Did you see Shide?

818
00:53:14,691 --> 00:53:15,959
Did you see Zhou Shuyi then?

819
00:53:18,528 --> 00:53:20,063
What are you doing?

820
00:53:20,063 --> 00:53:21,331
Let's leave together.

821
00:53:22,165 --> 00:53:22,799
Your hand.

822
00:53:23,333 --> 00:53:24,901
Stop following me.

823
00:53:24,901 --> 00:53:26,169
Stop dragging me.

824
00:53:26,169 --> 00:53:27,504
Let go of me.

825
00:53:28,538 --> 00:53:30,207
Have you lost your mind?

826
00:53:40,283 --> 00:53:42,085
This is ridiculous.

827
00:53:42,085 --> 00:53:44,621
Why would they hide the clue
in the health center?

828
00:53:45,555 --> 00:53:46,289
Yeah.

829
00:53:47,290 --> 00:53:48,558
This is ridiculous.

830
00:53:52,796 --> 00:53:54,097
