836
00:54:07,510 --> 00:54:08,545
Are you a fool?

837
00:54:14,517 --> 00:54:15,986
Don't be scared!

838
00:54:17,787 --> 00:54:18,655
Gao Shide, let's run!

839
00:54:18,655 --> 00:54:20,924
Calm down.

840
00:54:36,006 --> 00:54:36,906
Hello?

841
00:54:36,906 --> 00:54:40,010
