846
00:54:47,317 --> 00:54:48,151
Hello?

847
00:54:48,918 --> 00:54:49,986
Is anyone there?

848
00:54:52,656 --> 00:54:54,424
Isn't this your territory?

849
00:54:54,424 --> 00:54:56,393
Think of something.

850
00:54:56,393 --> 00:54:58,228
What can I think of?

851
00:54:58,228 --> 00:54:59,896
We don't have our phones.

852
00:55:00,897 --> 00:55:02,465
