853
00:55:08,138 --> 00:55:09,906
The telephone isn't working.

854
00:55:13,209 --> 00:55:15,178
There's a computer here.

855
00:55:15,979 --> 00:55:17,881
I think it's connected to the Wi-Fi.

856
00:55:17,881 --> 00:55:20,317
We can tell Zhengwen to help us out.

857
00:55:23,186 --> 00:55:24,821
A password?

858
00:55:36,900 --> 00:55:37,500
Are you hungry?

859
00:55:46,309 --> 00:55:47,210
Got it.

860
00:55:53,416 --> 00:55:55,085
