870
00:56:27,717 --> 00:56:28,852
How is that possible?

871
00:56:32,122 --> 00:56:33,089
Yeah.

872
00:56:33,957 --> 00:56:35,091
How is that possible?

873
00:56:38,361 --> 00:56:39,763
You must be joking, right?

874
00:56:39,763 --> 00:56:41,297
Of course I'm joking.

875
00:56:43,700 --> 00:56:46,002
