with Shouyi.

876
00:56:46,903 --> 00:56:48,238
You're so petty.

877
00:56:50,373 --> 00:56:52,041
You're stubborn.

878
00:57:07,223 --> 00:57:08,858
It'll be done in a second.

879
00:57:24,374 --> 00:57:26,075
Don't tell me this is the last one?

880
00:57:30,947 --> 00:57:32,816
You're so long-winded. Just eat up.

881
00:57:36,719 --> 00:57:38,288
We should eat together.

882
00:57:41,090 --> 00:57:43,426
It's better for one to be full
than for two to be starving.

883
00:57:43,860 --> 00:57:46,830
It's better for two to starve a little
than for one to die of starvation.

884
00:57:47,697 --> 00:57:49,432
There's no need to do this.

885
00:57:50,700 --> 00:57:51,801
We're friends, right?

886
00:57:56,339 --> 00:57:57,140
Fine.

887
00:58:09,018 --> 00:58:10,620
Let me tell you this.
Although we're friends,

888
00:58:10,620 --> 00:58:12,622
