I won't compete with you.

889
00:58:12,622 --> 00:58:13,890
I won't keep losing to you.

890
00:58:17,026 --> 00:58:18,661
I won't give you a chance to win.

891
00:58:44,420 --> 00:58:45,555
Let's not go there.

892
00:58:45,555 --> 00:58:46,389
This is the place.

893
00:58:46,389 --> 00:58:47,090
Wait.

894
00:58:47,090 --> 00:58:49,125
My juniors didn't tell me
about this area.

895
00:58:49,459 --> 00:58:50,059
Don't do this.

896
00:58:50,059 --> 00:58:51,094
I'm begging you.

897
00:58:51,094 --> 00:58:52,328
-It's on the map.
-Stop messing around.

898
00:58:52,328 --> 00:58:53,530
Let's leave, okay?

899
00:58:53,530 --> 00:58:53,963
Come on.

900
00:58:56,499 --> 00:58:58,067
What is that?

901
00:59:01,905 --> 00:59:02,872
That's fake.

902
00:59:02,872 --> 00:59:04,007
I can tell it's a student.

903
00:59:04,007 --> 00:59:04,974
Wait.

904
00:59:04,974 --> 00:59:05,542
That's impossible.

905
00:59:05,542 --> 00:59:06,209
It's one of our juniors.

906
00:59:09,479 --> 00:59:10,847
You guys are going overboard here.

907
00:59:11,047 --> 00:59:12,515
Back off!

908
00:59:13,149 --> 00:59:13,983
Let's leave this place.

909
00:59:13,983 --> 00:59:14,817
Come on.

910
00:59:16,886 --> 00:59:19,689
Don't leave.

911
00:59:19,689 --> 00:59:21,391
I'm bored.

912
00:59:21,391 --> 00:59:23,326
Play with me.

913
00:59:23,326 --> 00:59:25,061
I'll carry you. Come on.

914
00:59:40,243 --> 00:59:41,878
You did look convincing as a ghost.

915
00:59:41,878 --> 00:59:42,946
Fang Zhengwen,

916
00:59:42,946 --> 00:59:43,913
you better watch out!

917
00:59:45,815 --> 00:59:47,250
(My goodness.)

918
00:59:47,450 --> 00:59:49,018
(I have to spend the night
in a terrifying place like this)

919
00:59:49,018 --> 00:59:51,187
(when this is my first time
spending the night outside?)

920
00:59:51,955 --> 00:59:52,589
Gao Shide.

921
00:59:55,325 --> 00:59:56,626
Are you scared?

922
00:59:56,626 --> 00:59:57,927
Do you dare to sleep alone?

923
00:59:58,962 --> 00:59:59,429
Oh.

924
01:00:00,863 --> 01:00:02,065
I don't.

925
01:00:02,065 --> 01:00:03,032
