926
01:00:03,032 --> 01:00:04,300
No one will mock their friends.

927
01:00:05,068 --> 01:00:06,135
Come here.

928
01:00:06,769 --> 01:00:07,604
I'll protect you.

929
01:00:13,409 --> 01:00:15,244
Move your bed nearer.

930
01:00:15,244 --> 01:00:16,412
I'll chat with you.

931
01:00:26,589 --> 01:00:27,757
What should we chat about?

932
01:00:30,660 --> 01:00:32,195
Hmm.

933
01:00:33,329 --> 01:00:35,698
What kind of person do you like?

934
01:00:46,542 --> 01:00:47,377
That person...

935
01:00:52,815 --> 01:00:54,283
He's adorable.

936
01:00:58,087 --> 01:00:59,489
Some people

937
01:01:01,357 --> 01:01:03,159
think that he's arrogant,

938
01:01:03,159 --> 01:01:04,827
cocky, and narcissistic.

939
01:01:06,229 --> 01:01:07,497
But to me,

940
01:01:09,298 --> 01:01:10,800
he's just cute.

941
01:01:12,135 --> 01:01:13,970
Even his flaws are
strengths to you, huh?

942
01:01:14,904 --> 01:01:16,372
I guess it's true love.

943
01:01:18,408 --> 01:01:19,609
Maybe.

944
01:01:23,079 --> 01:01:25,448
Although he's proud and stubborn,

945
01:01:26,949 --> 01:01:28,885
he treats his friends nicely.

946
01:01:30,520 --> 01:01:32,188
He would endure hardships

947
01:01:32,622 --> 01:01:33,823
to protect his friends.

948
01:01:34,390 --> 01:01:35,525
He's pretty loyal, huh?

949
01:01:35,925 --> 01:01:37,493
I guess that counts as a strength.

950
01:01:39,262 --> 01:01:40,963
He has plenty of other strengths too.

951
01:01:43,232 --> 01:01:45,201
Don't you plan to confess to him?

952
01:01:54,577 --> 01:01:56,279
I don't plan to ruin

953
01:01:56,679 --> 01:01:58,214
