I spent so much effort to obtain.

954
01:02:01,951 --> 01:02:03,753
I guess both of us are unlucky.

955
01:02:04,787 --> 01:02:06,022
I understand your feelings.

956
01:02:08,825 --> 01:02:10,660
I've already gotten over it.

957
01:02:11,928 --> 01:02:13,863
But now, you're still dwelling on it.

958
01:02:13,863 --> 01:02:14,697
Poor guy.

959
01:02:18,735 --> 01:02:21,170
Come to me if you need someone
to listen to you.

960
01:02:21,637 --> 01:02:22,839
I'll listen,

961
01:02:23,439 --> 01:02:24,807
and I'll keep it a secret.

962
01:02:26,609 --> 01:02:27,443
Don't stand on ceremony.

963
01:02:33,149 --> 01:02:34,117
Thank you.

964
01:02:34,650 --> 01:02:36,486
Your crush is tasteless

965
01:02:36,486 --> 01:02:38,321
for not liking you.

966
01:02:40,356 --> 01:02:41,324
And, he's lucky

967
01:02:41,324 --> 01:02:42,759
that you have a crush on him.

968
01:02:45,828 --> 01:02:47,263
You're a good guy.

969
01:02:55,972 --> 01:02:56,906
Gao Shide,

970
01:02:57,406 --> 01:02:58,608
sing a song for me.

971
01:03:00,643 --> 01:03:01,744
You want me to sing?

972
01:03:04,113 --> 01:03:05,782
I have to listen to songs
before I go to bed.

973
01:03:07,984 --> 01:03:09,285
Hurry and sing.

974
01:03:24,700 --> 01:03:30,673
The tide that has not receded

975
01:03:34,644 --> 01:03:40,016
Summer is hot because of you

976
01:03:42,151 --> 01:03:44,453
Love is hiding inside you

977
01:03:44,453 --> 01:03:46,823
Going in circles

978
01:03:47,190 --> 01:03:52,028
It's ambiguous whether I say it or not

979
01:03:52,428 --> 01:03:59,969
I want you to know that
you don't need to wait until tomorrow

980
01:04:00,503 --> 01:04:02,338
Great lyrics.

981
01:04:03,139 --> 01:04:04,774
You do have a great sense.

982
01:04:12,949 --> 01:04:14,050
Go on.

983
01:04:14,050 --> 01:04:15,218
That was nice.

984
01:04:18,988 --> 01:04:21,023
This is your second time
complimenting me.

985
01:04:23,993 --> 01:04:25,761
Please continue your singing.

986
01:04:35,671 --> 01:04:36,138
Okay.

987
01:04:42,445 --> 01:04:43,512
Here I go.

988
01:04:47,583 --> 01:04:49,352
If you wish

989
01:04:50,987 --> 01:04:55,725
Let the rain wash away
a certain habit gently

990
01:04:55,992 --> 01:05:00,963
Peace of mind isn't everything

991
01:05:00,963 --> 01:05:03,633
The call, which was never there

992
01:05:03,766 --> 01:05:06,636
Awakened me

993
01:05:06,636 --> 01:05:10,172
I just want to hear about
your views on love

994
01:05:10,172 --> 01:05:14,939
Blue is romantic to you

995
01:05:14,940 --> 01:05:19,150
Maybe my hallucination gave me more than just peace of mind

996
01:05:19,150 --> 01:05:22,490
The sun shining upon the sea

997
01:05:22,490 --> 01:05:27,400
You're inside my heart

998
01:05:30,280 --> 01:05:34,360
Your breath and sound

999
01:05:34,360 --> 01:05:38,650
The closest distance in total silence

1000
01:05:38,650 --> 01:05:40,860
Time, stopped by stuffiness

1001
01:05:40,860 --> 01:05:43,360
A sun shower

1002
01:05:43,360 --> 01:05:49,110
I can't stop thinking about you

1003
01:05:52,320 --> 01:05:56,820
Let the rain wash away a certain habit gently

1004
01:05:56,820 --> 01:06:01,360
Peace of mind isn't everything

1005
01:06:01,360 --> 01:06:04,400
The call, which was never there

1006
01:06:04,400 --> 01:06:07,320
Awakened me

1007
01:06:07,320 --> 01:06:10,820
I just want to hear about your views on love

1008
01:06:10,820 --> 01:06:15,450
Blue is romantic to you

1009
01:06:15,450 --> 01:06:20,070
Please stop relieving me with hallucinations

1010
01:06:20,309 --> 01:06:22,645
(Closing the distance
between us in secret.)

1011
01:06:26,282 --> 01:06:28,017
(Then asking you)

1012
01:06:28,884 --> 01:06:31,721
(whether we can
keep on going like this.)

1013
01:06:35,291 --> 01:06:40,162
(It's a shame that I still
don't have the courage to say it out.)

1014
01:07:29,600 --> 01:07:36,500
(Password, Ee1I)

1015
01:07:36,786 --> 01:07:38,921
Alright. Now, let's welcome

1016
01:07:38,921 --> 01:07:41,791
our hot and scary female ghost,

1017
01:07:41,791 --> 01:07:43,592
Yuxin.

1018
01:07:45,828 --> 01:07:47,596
You were very convincing as a ghost.

1019
01:07:48,631 --> 01:07:49,698
I'll beat you up.

1020
01:07:51,567 --> 01:07:52,601
Where's Shuyi?

1021
01:07:54,303 --> 01:07:55,704
I didn't see him.

1022
01:07:56,105 --> 01:07:57,473
Didn't he return with you?

1023
01:07:58,808 --> 01:08:00,242
I thought he was behind you.

1024
01:08:02,278 --> 01:08:03,512
That's impossible.

1025
01:08:03,813 --> 01:08:04,847
Shide hasn't returned yet.

1026
01:08:04,847 --> 01:08:07,716
Has anyone seen Shuyi and Shide?

1027
01:08:10,219 --> 01:08:12,755
They're fine. They just texted me.

1028
01:08:12,755 --> 01:08:15,958
They left first because they thought
the event was boring.

1029
01:08:15,958 --> 01:08:17,626
Did you guys think it's boring?

1030
01:08:18,427 --> 01:08:20,196
(It's boring here.)

1031
01:08:20,196 --> 01:08:21,497
(Zhou Shuyi and I will leave first.)

1032
01:08:21,497 --> 01:08:22,731
(Keep our phones for us.)

1033
01:08:22,731 --> 01:08:23,499
(We'll take them tomorrow.)

1034
01:08:23,499 --> 01:08:25,034
Zhou Shuyi again?

1035
01:08:26,702 --> 01:08:29,004
Since when did they become
a pair of conjoined twins?

1036
01:08:29,705 --> 01:08:30,940
How's your leg?

1037
01:08:30,940 --> 01:08:31,841
"We?"

1038
01:08:33,042 --> 01:08:34,477
I'm fine.

1039
01:08:35,077 --> 01:08:36,345
Coward.

1040
01:08:36,345 --> 01:08:38,208
It's late and time to end this.

1041
01:08:38,314 --> 01:08:40,449
Everyone, head back
and rest early, okay?

1042
01:10:05,134 --> 01:10:06,035
You...

1043
01:10:08,971 --> 01:10:10,206
