1044
01:10:10,206 --> 01:10:10,806
Get out.

1045
01:10:18,647 --> 01:10:19,582
Beg me.

1046
01:10:22,551 --> 01:10:23,652
Get out.

1047
01:10:26,021 --> 01:10:27,223
Please.

1048
01:10:58,754 --> 01:11:00,322
Yesterday,

1049
01:11:02,825 --> 01:11:03,993
when I said I have a crush on you,

1050
01:11:06,528 --> 01:11:07,363
I wasn't lying.

1051
01:11:11,333 --> 01:11:13,802
I wasn't lying when I said I would
take advantage of the situation.

1052
01:11:16,972 --> 01:11:18,774
But I wouldn't do that to you.

1053
01:11:23,279 --> 01:11:24,680
You said

1054
01:11:27,283 --> 01:11:30,452
the person whom I had a crush on
is lucky.

1055
01:11:34,123 --> 01:11:36,091
However, that luck of mine

1056
01:11:37,793 --> 01:11:39,194
has always been with you.

1057
01:11:44,767 --> 01:11:46,702
It's a shame that you'll never know.

1058
01:12:17,733 --> 01:12:18,701
Zhou Shuyi,

1059
01:12:22,538 --> 01:12:23,639
I like you.

1060
01:13:32,341 --> 01:13:33,108
