1067
01:13:49,725 --> 01:13:51,326
(We were supposed
to have lunch together.)

1068
01:13:51,326 --> 01:13:52,094
(Did you forget?)

1069
01:13:52,094 --> 01:13:53,128
What's the matter?

1070
01:13:53,762 --> 01:13:54,430
It's nothing.

1071
01:13:54,930 --> 01:13:55,631
What would you like to eat?

1072
01:13:56,565 --> 01:13:57,933
-Let me take a look.
-Okay.

1073
01:14:11,947 --> 01:14:13,215
Well.

1074
01:14:15,617 --> 01:14:17,820
Do you guys know where Shuyi is?

1075
01:14:25,627 --> 01:14:26,795
What's the matter?

1076
01:14:26,795 --> 01:14:28,797
I plan to learn how to swim lately.

1077
01:14:28,797 --> 01:14:31,667
You guys are excellent swimmers.

1078
01:14:31,667 --> 01:14:33,202
I wish to take photos

1079
01:14:33,202 --> 01:14:35,270
