1083
01:14:43,178 --> 01:14:44,346
When I'm free,

1084
01:14:44,346 --> 01:14:45,514
I'll catch a baseball match

1085
01:14:45,514 --> 01:14:47,249
and cheer for the players.

1086
01:14:48,150 --> 01:14:49,184
Swimming.

1087
01:14:49,184 --> 01:14:50,586
Swimming is fine.

1088
01:14:51,186 --> 01:14:51,854
Or,

1089
01:14:51,854 --> 01:14:53,589
should we play bowling?

1090
01:14:54,223 --> 01:14:55,390
Shuyi said

1091
01:14:56,225 --> 01:14:57,759
