1092
01:14:59,595 --> 01:15:01,964
A junior of mine has
fancied him for a long time.

1093
01:15:02,264 --> 01:15:03,932
That's why...

1094
01:15:06,535 --> 01:15:10,205
You and Shuyi are really close lately.

1095
01:15:10,205 --> 01:15:11,240
Are you two

1096
01:15:11,240 --> 01:15:12,441
merely good friends?

1097
01:15:13,542 --> 01:15:14,543
Is that so?

1098
01:15:15,711 --> 01:15:16,512
Yeah.

1099
01:15:17,546 --> 01:15:18,547
Friends.

1100
01:15:19,581 --> 01:15:21,016
We're just good friends.

1101
01:15:23,752 --> 01:15:24,786
Is that so?

1102
01:15:32,127 --> 01:15:33,395
I love shrimp.

1103
01:15:33,395 --> 01:15:34,530
What about you? Do you like it?

1104
01:15:34,530 --> 01:15:35,864
I do.

1105
01:15:58,921 --> 01:15:59,788
Here you go.

1106
01:16:01,356 --> 01:16:02,891
