1115
01:16:20,309 --> 01:16:22,244
Why don't we go there
together next time?

1116
01:16:22,744 --> 01:16:23,812
I'm busy tomorrow.

1117
01:16:23,812 --> 01:16:25,347
I can't join you tomorrow.

1118
01:16:29,918 --> 01:16:31,653
