1123
01:16:47,469 --> 01:16:50,238
Shuyi.

1124
01:16:51,206 --> 01:16:52,975
I...

1125
01:17:00,248 --> 01:17:01,316
No!

1126
01:17:05,253 --> 01:17:05,821
