1137
01:17:34,950 --> 01:17:35,784
Pick one.

1138
01:17:37,586 --> 01:17:38,720
Just support me.

1139
01:17:39,187 --> 01:17:39,921
Support me.

1140
01:17:48,597 --> 01:17:49,765
He's not a doctor.

1141
01:17:55,437 --> 01:17:56,138
Fine.

1142
01:17:56,638 --> 01:17:58,774
It's my break time anyway.

1143
01:17:59,374 --> 01:18:00,809
Who else can you blame
