1144
01:18:01,309 --> 01:18:02,344
Treat your own injury.

1145
01:18:03,178 --> 01:18:04,112
Where's the bandage?

1146
01:18:04,112 --> 01:18:04,913
I'll treat his injury.

1147
01:18:05,814 --> 01:18:07,182
I'm going to get it

1148
01:18:07,182 --> 01:18:08,250
