1149
01:18:09,317 --> 01:18:10,585
Is it at the warehouse?

1150
01:18:10,585 --> 01:18:11,720
Go now.

1151
01:18:37,212 --> 01:18:38,480
What are you looking at?

1152
01:18:39,181 --> 01:18:40,716
Seems like

1153
01:18:41,316 --> 01:18:42,584
I can rest at ease.

1154
01:18:45,987 --> 01:18:47,389
You're not as good as me.

1155
01:18:48,056 --> 01:18:49,491
You won't attract Shide's attention.

1156
01:18:49,725 --> 01:18:50,959
What do you mean by that?

1157
01:18:52,461 --> 01:18:54,463
Don't you know that men
can fall in love with men?

1158
01:18:54,863 --> 01:18:55,530
Kiddo.

1159
01:18:56,431 --> 01:18:57,432
So, you...

1160
01:18:57,432 --> 01:18:58,500
I can definitely win his heart.

1161
01:19:01,169 --> 01:19:02,137
Keep this a secret.

1162
01:19:03,105 --> 01:19:04,473
