1163
01:19:05,173 --> 01:19:06,408
Wish me luck.

1164
01:19:06,608 --> 01:19:07,843
Just you wish!

1165
01:19:08,376 --> 01:19:09,611
Why would I keep your secret?

1166
01:19:09,611 --> 01:19:10,712
Just give up.

1167
01:19:11,113 --> 01:19:13,115
Gao Shide said he had a crush on me.

1168
01:19:19,955 --> 01:19:22,257
I guess your secret

1169
01:19:22,958 --> 01:19:24,559
is no longer a secret.

1170
01:19:34,903 --> 01:19:35,837
Pei Shouyi.

1171
01:19:36,671 --> 01:19:37,672
