1172
01:19:38,907 --> 01:19:39,875
Don't go to him.

1173
01:19:53,922 --> 01:19:55,557
Tell him what's on your mind.

1174
01:19:56,925 --> 01:19:58,126
Don't leave any regrets behind.

1175
01:20:28,757 --> 01:20:29,558
What are you up to?

1176
01:20:43,338 --> 01:20:44,272
Gao Shide...

1177
01:20:44,539 --> 01:20:45,707
We can talk after I'm done
treating your injury.

1178
01:20:56,518 --> 01:20:58,453
I didn't expect myself
to fall for another man.

1179
01:21:09,698 --> 01:21:10,832
I know.

1180
01:21:19,741 --> 01:21:20,976
Gao Shide.

1181
01:21:21,109 --> 01:21:22,077
Try and stand up.

1182
01:21:28,850 --> 01:21:29,684
It's much better.

1183
01:21:32,487 --> 01:21:33,154
Thank you.

1184
01:21:39,060 --> 01:21:40,028
Zhou Shuyi.

1185
01:21:46,801 --> 01:21:48,436
Having a crush on you only concerns me.

1186
01:21:53,041 --> 01:21:54,276
It has nothing to do with you.

1187
01:21:59,281 --> 01:22:00,815
Forget what I said.

1188
01:22:01,600 --> 01:22:06,200
I never thought that

1189
01:22:06,920 --> 01:22:11,620
Letting go is more heartbreaking than breaking up

1190
01:22:14,229 --> 01:22:16,298
It has nothing to do with me?

1191
01:22:16,631 --> 01:22:17,732
You have a crush on me, you know?

1192
01:22:17,732 --> 01:22:19,234
How could it have nothing to do with me?

1193
01:22:36,584 --> 01:22:38,453
(Silly: our deal is over.)

1194
01:22:38,453 --> 01:22:39,988
(I will delete the video.)

1195
01:22:39,988 --> 01:22:42,190
(Thank you for your friendship
while it lasted.)

1196
01:22:42,190 --> 01:22:43,758
"While it lasted?"

1197
01:22:43,758 --> 01:22:45,961
Did I say that I would
sever my ties with you?

1198
01:22:46,261 --> 01:22:47,963
Fine. Let's not be friends then.

1199
01:22:47,963 --> 01:22:49,164
Who cares?

1200
01:23:54,708 --> 01:24:01,417
(Fool. Gao Shide.)

1201
01:24:23,825 --> 01:24:26,261
You should find him if you miss him.

1202
01:24:27,595 --> 01:24:29,531
Do you think I haven't tried that?

1203
01:24:31,566 --> 01:24:33,301
If so, why didn't you
ask him out directly?

1204
01:24:34,135 --> 01:24:34,736
Why should I?

1205
01:24:35,870 --> 01:24:38,473
If I do, he'll know that
I'm looking for him.

1206
01:24:38,840 --> 01:24:39,674
It'll be embarrassing.

1207
01:24:40,675 --> 01:24:41,910
Are you a kid?

1208
01:24:42,610 --> 01:24:44,012
You traveled around the academy

1209
01:24:44,012 --> 01:24:45,613
just so you could bump into him
by chance, right?

1210
01:24:46,948 --> 01:24:47,782
Can't I do so?

1211
01:24:49,918 --> 01:24:52,120
I thought it would be easy to locate
people since we have technology.

1212
01:24:52,687 --> 01:24:53,788
Now, I know

1213
01:24:53,788 --> 01:24:56,391
that you can't find anyone
if he wishes to hide.

1214
01:24:57,926 --> 01:24:59,761
How did he manage to find me
before this?

1215
01:25:00,161 --> 01:25:01,996
We majored in different courses.

1216
01:25:01,996 --> 01:25:03,698
Even so, I bumped into him every day.

1217
01:25:06,401 --> 01:25:08,236
Now that you mentioned it,
I remember something.

1218
01:25:08,236 --> 01:25:10,939
He's always by your side
no matter where you go.

1219
01:25:12,474 --> 01:25:14,375
He must be a stalker.

1220
01:25:14,609 --> 01:25:15,477
He's out of his mind.

1221
01:25:21,983 --> 01:25:23,985
Zhengwen told me

1222
01:25:23,985 --> 01:25:26,754
that you had feelings for me
before this, right?

1223
01:25:28,056 --> 01:25:29,190
It's all in the past now.

1224
01:25:31,159 --> 01:25:33,161
However, did you realize something?

1225
01:25:33,528 --> 01:25:35,230
The one who always stays by your side

1226
01:25:35,230 --> 01:25:36,097
is Gao Shide.

1227
01:25:38,967 --> 01:25:39,767
Shuyi,

1228
01:25:40,835 --> 01:25:42,537
did you fall for him?

1229
01:25:48,376 --> 01:25:50,011
Do the thing you're supposed to.

1230
01:25:51,212 --> 01:25:52,080
Good luck.

1231
01:26:11,332 --> 01:26:13,635
(Yi: Gao Shide, what are you doing?)

1232
01:26:13,835 --> 01:26:15,537
(Why couldn't I find you
no matter where I went?)

1233
01:26:20,542 --> 01:26:21,509
Gao Shide!

1234
01:26:22,610 --> 01:26:24,012
So, you were avoiding me, huh?

1235
01:26:24,512 --> 01:26:26,414
Are you tired of stalking me around now?

1236
01:26:29,751 --> 01:26:31,052
I deleted the video.

1237
01:26:31,052 --> 01:26:32,187
You can check my phone
if you don't trust me.

1238
01:26:33,688 --> 01:26:35,523
You threatened me with the video

1239
01:26:35,857 --> 01:26:37,358
and coerced me into being your attendant

1240
01:26:37,825 --> 01:26:39,360
because you were worried about me
after falling out of love.

1241
01:26:43,097 --> 01:26:45,466
You said the deal would be over
as long as I defeat you once

1242
01:26:46,801 --> 01:26:48,503
in order to shift
my attention away, right?

1243
01:26:48,503 --> 01:26:50,171
I'm not as good as you think.

1244
01:26:51,172 --> 01:26:52,807
I'm selfish too.

1245
01:26:54,943 --> 01:26:56,511
I did so to close the gap between us.

1246
01:26:57,111 --> 01:26:58,880
At least we can be friends
before graduating.

1247
01:26:59,614 --> 01:27:00,982
Are you a fool?

1248
01:27:00,982 --> 01:27:02,150
You only want to be friends?

1249
01:27:02,150 --> 01:27:04,052
Didn't you treat Jiang Yuxin
and Fang Zhengwen the same way?

1250
01:27:10,091 --> 01:27:11,259
If there's nothing else,
I'll make a move first.

1251
01:27:13,528 --> 01:27:15,063
Does your luck still belong to me?

1252
01:27:21,502 --> 01:27:23,504
When we were in the health center,

1253
01:27:23,504 --> 01:27:25,373
I said the person whom
you had a crush on is lucky.

1254
01:27:26,507 --> 01:27:28,443
When I was asleep, you said

1255
01:27:28,443 --> 01:27:30,511
that your luck has always been with me.

1256
01:27:33,147 --> 01:27:34,882
Is it still mine now?

1257
01:27:36,784 --> 01:27:37,885
Answer me.

1258
01:27:38,553 --> 01:27:39,520
Is it still mine?

1259
01:27:41,155 --> 01:27:42,557
It doesn't matter now.

1260
01:27:44,459 --> 01:27:46,127
Gao Shide, I'm serious.

1261
01:27:46,127 --> 01:27:47,462
Stop messing around.

1262
01:28:04,545 --> 01:28:05,546
Zhou Shuyi,

1263
01:28:06,581 --> 01:28:07,708
I'll get angry
if you keep being like this.

1264
01:28:07,749 --> 01:28:09,817
I should be the one
getting angry instead.

1265
01:28:09,817 --> 01:28:11,653
Does your luck still belong to me?

1266
01:28:11,653 --> 01:28:13,321
Or were you just joking?

1267
01:28:13,321 --> 01:28:14,922
Zhou Shuyi, what do you want?

1268
01:28:14,922 --> 01:28:16,524
Because I like you!

1269
01:28:26,834 --> 01:28:28,736
What about Jiang Yuxin then?

1270
01:28:28,736 --> 01:28:30,238
Didn't you say you wouldn't
fall for another man?

1271
01:28:30,238 --> 01:28:31,406
It's you.

1272
01:28:32,607 --> 01:28:33,941
I have to fall for you
whether I like it or not.

1273
01:28:40,515 --> 01:28:42,016
You don't trust me?

1274
01:28:42,583 --> 01:28:43,251
Fine.

1275
01:28:44,385 --> 01:28:45,853
What are you doing?

1276
01:28:46,521 --> 01:28:47,588
Since you don't trust me,

1277
01:28:47,588 --> 01:28:49,157
I can only prove it with my actions.

1278
01:28:49,157 --> 01:28:51,059
You'll trust me
once I discard this, right?

1279
01:28:51,726 --> 01:28:53,728
Discarding your lucky charm
doesn't mean anything.

1280
01:28:57,965 --> 01:28:58,966
I,

1281
01:28:58,966 --> 01:29:02,770
Zhou Shuyi, like Gao Shide!

1282
01:29:03,438 --> 01:29:05,840
I like him the most!

1283
01:29:06,441 --> 01:29:08,076
I like him so much!

1284
01:29:08,776 --> 01:29:12,680
I like him the most in the entire world!

1285
01:29:13,548 --> 01:29:15,850
I like him so much!

1286
01:29:17,685 --> 01:29:18,953
I like...

1287
01:29:21,622 --> 01:29:23,257
Do you trust me now?

1288
01:29:36,738 --> 01:29:38,539
What's mine will be mine.

1289
01:29:39,006 --> 01:29:40,875
It will always be mine.

1290
01:29:44,510 --> 01:29:46,010
If you wish

1291
01:29:46,040 --> 01:29:50,240
Let the rain wash away a certain habit gently

1292
01:29:51,100 --> 01:29:55,000
Peace of mind isn't everything

1293
01:29:55,790 --> 01:29:57,990
The call, which was never there

1294
01:29:58,810 --> 01:30:00,910
Awakened me

1295
01:30:01,420 --> 01:30:03,920
I just want to hear about your views on love

1296
01:30:04,780 --> 01:30:09,280
Blue is romantic to you

1297
01:30:09,860 --> 01:30:13,860
Maybe my hallucination gave me more than just peace of mind

1298
01:30:14,660 --> 01:30:16,860
The sun shining upon the sea

1299
01:30:17,570 --> 01:30:21,070
You're inside my heart

1300
01:30:23,251 --> 01:30:25,186
Was that your first kiss?

1301
01:30:25,210 --> 01:30:29,010
Your breath and sound

1302
01:30:29,700 --> 01:30:33,600
The closest distance in total silence

1303
01:30:33,995 --> 01:30:35,496
Who took your first kiss then?

1304
01:30:39,467 --> 01:30:41,035
It happened in the swimming pool.

1305
01:30:43,504 --> 01:30:45,106
That doesn't count.

1306
01:30:47,610 --> 01:30:51,510
Let the rain wash away a certain habit gently

1307
01:30:51,540 --> 01:30:59,780
(Whose concern is it
when you fall for someone?)

1308
01:30:59,810 --> 01:31:02,210
Awakened me

1309
01:31:02,260 --> 01:31:10,460
(Because it's you. I have to fall for
you no matter if I like it or not.)

1310
01:31:11,070 --> 01:31:15,370
Please stop relieving me with hallucinations

1311
01:31:15,990 --> 01:31:17,990
The sun shining upon the sea

1312
01:31:19,106 --> 01:31:19,874
Gao Shide.

1313
01:31:22,844 --> 01:31:24,345
Pei Shouyi.

1314
01:31:24,345 --> 01:31:26,481
Have you seen Gao Shide around?

1315
01:31:34,188 --> 01:31:35,723
Why are they not around?

1316
01:31:40,528 --> 01:31:42,163
I haven't told him yet.

1317
01:31:46,000 --> 01:31:47,368
I didn't expect him

1318
01:31:47,368 --> 01:31:49,537
to change entirely after dating me.

1319
01:31:50,171 --> 01:31:51,439
He would worry about my mother

1320
01:31:51,439 --> 01:31:52,673
and try to make her happy.

1321
01:31:54,909 --> 01:31:56,277
You have no idea how cute he is

1322
01:31:56,277 --> 01:31:58,412
when he's serious.

1323
01:31:58,412 --> 01:31:59,480
Enough.

1324
01:32:00,047 --> 01:32:01,649
Stop showing off.

1325
01:32:02,917 --> 01:32:04,118
Don't cross the line.

1326
01:32:07,255 --> 01:32:08,256
I don't know how to break it to him

1327
01:32:08,256 --> 01:32:10,091
