after graduating.

1328
01:32:10,091 --> 01:32:11,225
You're heading to America?

1329
01:32:15,162 --> 01:32:17,365
Why didn't you tell me about it?

1330
01:32:17,365 --> 01:32:18,466
You...

1331
01:32:19,000 --> 01:32:19,734
You even...

1332
01:32:21,435 --> 01:32:23,671
Even if you want
a long-distance relationship,

1333
01:32:23,671 --> 01:32:25,840
you should ask for my permission first.

1334
01:32:25,840 --> 01:32:27,608
Do you even respect me?

1335
01:32:27,608 --> 01:32:28,409
Wait.

1336
01:32:28,409 --> 01:32:29,176
Listen.

1337
01:32:30,177 --> 01:32:31,579
Shide.

1338
01:32:34,148 --> 01:32:35,483
Remember to buy me some cigarettes

1339
01:32:36,350 --> 01:32:37,251
from America.

1340
01:33:02,610 --> 01:33:03,878
So,

1341
01:33:03,878 --> 01:33:06,180
why are you heading to America?

1342
01:33:06,180 --> 01:33:07,949
My mother is remarrying.

1343
01:33:07,949 --> 01:33:09,684
Her partner is an American.

1344
01:33:09,684 --> 01:33:12,620
She'll move to America
after the wedding.

1345
01:33:12,620 --> 01:33:14,055
I need to attend her wedding

1346
01:33:14,722 --> 01:33:15,856
and assess

1347
01:33:15,856 --> 01:33:18,125
her relationship with my stepfather.

1348
01:33:18,859 --> 01:33:21,028
I'll use that chance to establish
a connection with him too.

1349
01:33:21,028 --> 01:33:22,263
After all,

1350
01:33:22,263 --> 01:33:23,664
we'll be a family in the future.

1351
01:33:25,266 --> 01:33:26,300
Oh.

1352
01:33:28,269 --> 01:33:29,937
You're my family too.

1353
01:33:32,607 --> 01:33:34,408
Any other questions?

1354
01:33:34,408 --> 01:33:35,943
How long will you be away?

1355
01:33:36,677 --> 01:33:38,646
Maybe a few months.

1356
01:33:43,284 --> 01:33:44,285
I never expected you to sulk

1357
01:33:44,285 --> 01:33:46,320
about it even though
it's only a few months.

1358
01:33:49,924 --> 01:33:52,960
Do you like me that much?

1359
01:33:52,960 --> 01:33:54,495
Go away.

1360
01:33:54,996 --> 01:33:56,263
Come to my place tonight.

1361
01:33:56,263 --> 01:33:57,231
No.

1362
01:33:57,231 --> 01:33:59,367
My mother wants to know you better.

1363
01:33:59,367 --> 01:34:00,635
You should tell me this first.

1364
01:34:00,635 --> 01:34:02,003
What's your answer?

1365
01:34:02,003 --> 01:34:03,170
Okay.

1366
01:34:20,454 --> 01:34:21,288
Cheers.

1367
01:34:27,395 --> 01:34:28,829
This is a nice place.

1368
01:34:32,033 --> 01:34:32,767
What?

1369
01:34:40,141 --> 01:34:42,877
My mother and I saw this
when we were shopping.

1370
01:34:42,877 --> 01:34:44,445
We thought it's suitable for you.

1371
01:34:47,615 --> 01:34:49,617
You're not allowed to take it off.

1372
01:34:56,891 --> 01:34:58,659
Not even when I take a bath?

1373
01:34:59,293 --> 01:35:00,127
A bath?

1374
01:35:02,329 --> 01:35:03,664
Fine.

1375
01:35:03,664 --> 01:35:04,865
